Konquest 0.11.0 Documentation

Public API of the Konquest plugin for Spigot Minecraft

Konquest is in beta and is always seeking to improve. Expect bugs and occasional issues. Please provide API feedback or requests on GitHub and use the API label.

For more information about Konquest, review the Wiki or join the Discord, link in the Wiki.

Packages
Package
Description
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api
The base API package for Konquest.
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api.event
The event package includes events that can be handled just like Bukkit events.
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api.event.camp
Events related to barbarian camps.
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api.event.player
Events related to players.
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api.event.ruin
Events related to ruins.
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api.event.territory
Events related to all territories.
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api.event.town
Events related to towns.
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api.manager
The manager package provides specialized interfaces for specific features in Konquest.
com.github.rumsfield.konquest.api.model
The model package offers lower-level object interfaces that are managed by the managers.
